text: Oobleck may refer to: * Oobleck (non-Newtonian fluid), made of cornstarch and water ==Arts and entertainment== * Oobleck, a fictional green substance in the Dr. Seuss book Bartholomew and the Oobleck * Theater Oobleck, a theater company based in Chicago, US * Dr. Bartholomew Oobleck, a character from the animated series RWBY
title: Oobleck
